# Step 1: Project Setup

## Description
Set up your Azure environment and initialize your GitHub repository.

---

## Azure Setup

1. Sign in to https://portal.azure.com
2. Create a new **Resource Group** to organize your resources.
3. Create an **Azure App Service** to host your POS web application.
4. Create an **Azure SQL Database** to store transaction data.
5. Set up **Azure Event Hub** to stream transaction events for analytics.

---

## GitHub Repository Setup

1. Create a new repository named `CloudPOS-Insight` on GitHub.
2. Clone the repository locally:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/<your-username>/CloudPOS-Insight.git
   cd CloudPOS-Insight
   ```
